data.description: Two story, three bedroom two and a half bath home. All bedrooms are on second floor; which allows for spacious living and dinning on the primary floor. Spacious kitchen with plenty of cabinets, a walk in pantry and wash room located where noise doesn't interfere with watching your favorite TV program. Newly designed interior and exterior color pallets, that make seamless transition with furniture décor for years to come. Builder offers a 1-2-10 year warranty, move in package. ** see attachments for floor plan layout. Call today for details and more information (realtors see agent remarks)
